准入查询制度的情形的，将依法依规予以处理。 下一步，教育部将指导各省级教育行政部门、部门教育司（局）和教育部直属高校做好教职员工准入查询工作。督促各地积极宣传解读相关政策，营造推进教职员工准入查询工作的良好环境；监督指导本区域准入查询工作的实施，规范查询流程，定期开展检查；严格遵守个人信息保护相关规定，指导相关单位和人员加强信息管理工作，不得侵害查询对象个人隐私和其他合法权利。教育部：加强师德师风建设，推开教职工准入查询工作"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-308ff836a7e1955ec2fd024cb0397834_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "40 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/596674058"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I0ZTszsSbt5MgEAMaCDk0ODc1MTc1ILergqIGMAE4lwFAHHIJNTk2Njc0MDU4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "29_1681974161.0723014", "card_id": "Q_596479564", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 75}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "井上雄彦编剧、执导的动画电影《灌篮高手》内地上映，你有哪些观后感或想说的？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "动画电影《灌篮高手》于 2023 年 4 月 20 日在中国内地上映。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-ba2812a0c0d47a8eaeb66921ff6cad21_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "38 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/596479564"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I0ZTszsSbt5MgEAMaCDk0ODMyMDMwIOfA/aEGMAE4iAFAHXIJNTk2NDc5NTY0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "30_1681974161.0734372", "card_id": "Q_596140263", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 74}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "「发疯」可以被看作是一种管理情绪的方式吗？如何科学地管理个人情绪？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-62db36626bcaaac3cb314944d7b0c2f2_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "35 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/5961402